                TO XDJL409C-O-IDSTRY-GROUP-NAME
      *@      산업관리한도
              COMPUTE XDJL409C-O-IDSTRY-PER-MGT-LIMT
                    = XQJL009I-O-IDSTRY-MGT-CLAM / 1000000
      *@      산업익스포져
              COMPUTE XDJL409C-O-IDSTRY-PER-EXPSR
                    = XQJL009I-O-TE-LIMT-AUC / 1000000
      *@      변경전여신성관리한도
              MOVE ZERO
                TO XDJL409C-O-MODFI-BLI-MGT-LIMT
      *@      변경전시장성관리한도
              MOVE ZERO
                TO XDJL409C-O-MODFI-BM-MGT-LIMT
